'''Philip Amara''', called '''Phil''' for short, was an editor for [[Dark Horse Comics]] beginning in [[1995]]. He served as editor for several ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars comic books|comics]], including "[[Hoth (comic story)|Hoth]]" and "[[Fortune, Fate, and the Natural History of the Sarlacc]]," featured in ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' [[Star Wars Tales 5|#5]] and [[Star Wars Tales 6|#6]] respectively. Since then, Amara left Dark Horse to work on projects of his own creation.

